  "lyrics": "Seems like yesterday we used to care It seems like yesterday we used to not stare\nSeems like yesterday we used to care If our other person was going down before\nus But now we're just trippin' every motherfuck\naround Hoping they fall before we fall\nAin't trying to help no one at all Seems like yesterday man we all could ball\nNow we're just individualized inside our own pancake of life\nAnd making the shapes that we see If we don't agree with anyone, fuck them\nI don't even care You should come around and hug your fam\nYou should come around and be there I swear if you do that you'll find energy\nIt's called happiness in the great beyond It seems like yesterday all we had was really\nsmall troubles Yesterday it all seemed small, yeah\nIt seems like yesterday I could dream higher, feel brighter\nNow you're saying nah, nah, nah It's better now for you there from the storm\nFifteen years in the game Can't give me nothing recognition\nAll I'm feeling from you is shame I'm sorry you would hate yourself in that\nname, that frame It seems like yesterday you were telling\nme you'll love me forever And then your name would never be the same\nYou wanna take it back, you can't do that You wanna tell me I'm not a part of you\nWell fucking screw that, you hear me You hear it from the beginning\nHe's mine from the end of the mental thoughts We're just beginning again\nAnd you wanna look back to yesterday as it's not your friend\nReframe your life, you hear me Reframe the thing you want from you\nIt's not scary, it seems like yesterday We cared about what you had to say\nBeing creative in our own way Seems like yesterday I was okay with me\nI was okay\nNow the dark hit you right in the heart And you're sorry you didn't do this mistake\nFor the regret from your heart You should have been there from the start\nInstead you ink me in over glass beyond I can't see you my friend when you're so\nfucking mean It seems like yesterday you wanted my dream\nYou wanted me on your team It seems like yesterday it was all a dream\nNow I'm sitting there looking at Nelly Tim McGraw saying man, Im kinda funny\nLost my life, my dream Everything yesterday it seemed so complete\nNow I seem like it's just crumbled in the ocean of time\nAnd you're still on my mind\nAll the trips and all the fiends and the scenes Bring me closer to reality\nIt seems like yesterday I wasn't just a name in your book\nA reality, a fatality to write the hook\nBitch I told you I was still here until you told me I wasn't\nOh no, oh no",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 17.3799991607666,
      "text": "Seems like yesterday we used to care It seems like yesterday we used to not stare",
      "start": 10.979999542236328
    },
    {
      "end": 22.639999389648438,
      "text": "Seems like yesterday we used to care If our other person was going down before",
      "start": 17.440000534057617
    },
    {
      "end": 25.360000610351562,
      "text": "us But now we're just trippin' every motherfuck",
      "start": 22.639999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 29.639999389648438,
      "text": "around Hoping they fall before we fall",
      "start": 25.860000610351562
    },
    {
      "end": 35.84000015258789,
      "text": "Ain't trying to help no one at all Seems like yesterday man we all could ball",
      "start": 29.639999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 40.099998474121094,
      "text": "Now we're just individualized inside our own pancake of life",
      "start": 35.97999954223633
    },
    {
      "end": 45.34000015258789,
      "text": "And making the shapes that we see If we don't agree with anyone, fuck them",
      "start": 40.099998474121094
    },
    {
      "end": 49.81999969482422,
      "text": "I don't even care You should come around and hug your fam",
      "start": 45.34000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 56,
      "text": "You should come around and be there I swear if you do that you'll find energy",
      "start": 51.060001373291016
    },
    {
      "end": 66.37999725341797,
      "text": "It's called happiness in the great beyond It seems like yesterday all we had was really",
      "start": 56
    },
    {
      "end": 72,
      "text": "small troubles Yesterday it all seemed small, yeah",
      "start": 66.37999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 83.54000091552734,
      "text": "It seems like yesterday I could dream higher, feel brighter",
      "start": 72
    },
    {
      "end": 89.77999877929688,
      "text": "Now you're saying nah, nah, nah It's better now for you there from the storm",
      "start": 84.41999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 93.66000366210938,
      "text": "Fifteen years in the game Can't give me nothing recognition",
      "start": 89.81999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 98.95999908447266,
      "text": "All I'm feeling from you is shame I'm sorry you would hate yourself in that",
      "start": 93.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 104.18000030517578,
      "text": "name, that frame It seems like yesterday you were telling",
      "start": 98.95999908447266
    },
    {
      "end": 108.0199966430664,
      "text": "me you'll love me forever And then your name would never be the same",
      "start": 104.18000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 112.86000061035156,
      "text": "You wanna take it back, you can't do that You wanna tell me I'm not a part of you",
      "start": 108.0199966430664
    },
    {
      "end": 116.73999786376953,
      "text": "Well fucking screw that, you hear me You hear it from the beginning",
      "start": 112.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 121.80000305175781,
      "text": "He's mine from the end of the mental thoughts We're just beginning again",
      "start": 116.73999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 126.45999908447266,
      "text": "And you wanna look back to yesterday as it's not your friend",
      "start": 122
    },
    {
      "end": 131.22000122070312,
      "text": "Reframe your life, you hear me Reframe the thing you want from you",
      "start": 126.54000091552734
    },
    {
      "end": 139.82000732421875,
      "text": "It's not scary, it seems like yesterday We cared about what you had to say",
      "start": 131.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 152.22000122070312,
      "text": "Being creative in our own way Seems like yesterday I was okay with me",
      "start": 139.82000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 155.1999969482422,
      "text": "I was okay",
      "start": 152.82000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 165.9199981689453,
      "text": "Now the dark hit you right in the heart And you're sorry you didn't do this mistake",
      "start": 155.82000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 169.36000061035156,
      "text": "For the regret from your heart You should have been there from the start",
      "start": 165.9199981689453
    },
    {
      "end": 175.33999633789062,
      "text": "Instead you ink me in over glass beyond I can't see you my friend when you're so",
      "start": 169.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 181.86000061035156,
      "text": "fucking mean It seems like yesterday you wanted my dream",
      "start": 175.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 191.5800018310547,
      "text": "You wanted me on your team It seems like yesterday it was all a dream",
      "start": 182.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 197.66000366210938,
      "text": "Now I'm sitting there looking at Nelly Tim McGraw saying man, Im kinda funny",
      "start": 191.5800018310547
    },
    {
      "end": 202.05999755859375,
      "text": "Lost my life, my dream Everything yesterday it seemed so complete",
      "start": 197.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 205.8800048828125,
      "text": "Now I seem like it's just crumbled in the ocean of time",
      "start": 202.05999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 209.9600067138672,
      "text": "And you're still on my mind",
      "start": 206.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 218.3000030517578,
      "text": "All the trips and all the fiends and the scenes Bring me closer to reality",
      "start": 209.9600067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 224.6199951171875,
      "text": "It seems like yesterday I wasn't just a name in your book",
      "start": 218.3000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 229.77999877929688,
      "text": "A reality, a fatality to write the hook",
      "start": 224.75999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 234.74000549316406,
      "text": "Bitch I told you I was still here until you told me I wasn't",
      "start": 229.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 237.72000122070312,
      "text": "Oh no, oh no",
      "start": 234.74000549316406
    }
